OL,3,CEx-teacher and football coach jailed
OL,4,Cfor abuse of boys
OL,6,FA former football coach and teacher
OL,7,Fwho sexually abused two boys has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FJohn Staveley, 55, met one of his
OL,11,Fvictims while working as a coach. The
OL,12,Fother was abused on a school trip
OL,13,Fwhile Staveley was working as a
OL,14,Fprimary teacher.
OL,16,FThe abuse began in the late 1990s, but
OL,17,FStaveley was only arrested after the
OL,18,Ffirst victim reported what had
OL,19,Fhappened to the NSPCC in 2020.
