OL,3,CEx-teacher and football coach jailed
OL,4,Cfor abuse of boys
OL,6,FDetectives went on to gather witness
OL,7,Fstatements and screenshots of social
OL,8,Fmedia messages to help convict
OL,9,FStaveley.
OL,11,FHe was found guilty of nine counts of
OL,12,Fgross indecency with a boy under 14,
OL,13,Ftwo of indecent assault on a boy under
OL,14,F16 and one count of causing or
OL,15,Finciting a boy under 13 to engage in
OL,16,Fsexual activity.
OL,18,FStaveley, of Hale Hill Lane, was
OL,19,Fjailed for nine-and-a-half years at
OL,20,FSheffield Crown Court and placed on
OL,21,Fthe Sex Offenders' Register for life.
