OL,3,CEx-teacher and football coach jailed
OL,4,Cfor abuse of boys
OL,6,FDet Con Mike Tilley, of South
OL,7,FYorkshire Police, said: "Staveley
OL,8,Fabused his position as a mentor and
OL,9,Fguide to young children in sports and
OL,10,Feducational settings.
OL,12,F"He should have been someone his
OL,13,Fvictims were able to trust but instead
OL,14,Fhe exploited them, took advantage of
OL,15,Fthem and abused them for his own
OL,16,Fsexual gratification.
OL,18,F"I really want to commend his victims
OL,19,Ffor coming forward and telling us
OL,20,Fabout their harrowing and horrific
OL,21,Fexperiences as children."
